nodes.text: Supervisor was a job title held by individuals who supervised projects. Lee Skillen acted as the supervisor of Ohnaka Transport Solutions when its founder Hondo Ohnaka was offworld. The protocol droid G1-MD also assisted with supervising the company. Sava Toob-Nix of the University of Bar'leth personally supervised the studies of Chelli Aphra so that he could ensure she failed at becoming a doctor.
